snippet.title: PAYDAY 2: The Biker Packs Trailer
snippet.description:
Playable at E3 in Los Angeles starting Tuesday 14th!

In order of appearance:
RON PERLMAN as Rust
ANDY MCPHEE as Bartender
TRENTON ROSTEDT as Young Biker
BOKEEM WOODBINE as The Elephant
MARTIN KOVE as Old Biker
ERIC ETEBARI as Dallas
DAMION POITIER as Chains
DRAGOMIR MRSIC as Dragan

The Biker Packs are released on June 16th.
